---
const M = '/assets/media/projects/web-dev/boda-lis-pavlos';
---

<section class="blp-project relative container mx-auto flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 py-4">
  <div class="project-summary-card blp-card">
    <div class="blp-card-inner flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h1 class="font-display m-0 text-4xl uppercase">Boda Lis &amp; Pavlos</h1>

      <div class="blp-copy">
        <p>
          For this collaboration with La Invitación de Liana, I created a wedding website that
          celebrates both craftsmanship and digital elegance. Designed around the couple's vision, the
          site features a rich blend of soft animations and personalized illustrations, adding charm
          and personality to every section. Guests can explore the wedding details in an aesthetically
          balanced layout. A secure password-protected access ensures the privacy of all information,
          making the experience both intimate and exclusive.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between">
        <div class="md:w-8/12">
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl tracking-wide uppercase">Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="blp-copy">
            HTML, CSS, JavaScript development, server-side setup, custom illustration integration,
            hosting and domain configuration, website launch, post-launch support.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-4/12 md:pl-10 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl tracking-wide uppercase">URL</h2>
            <a href="https://pavlosandlis.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="blp-copy text-inherit">
              pavlosandlis.com
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl tracking-wide uppercase">Credits</h2>
            <p class="blp-copy">Illustrations by La Invitación de Liana</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex justify-center">
    <img src={`${M}/bodalp-desktop1-960.avif`} alt="Boda Lis & Pavlos mockup" class="first-project-image border-round-xl block h-auto w-full max-w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
  </div>

  <div class="blp-editorial flex flex-col gap-4 text-[var(--interactive-primary)]">
    <p>
      Fully bilingual, the website allows both local and international guests to navigate seamlessly in
      their preferred language. The site provides a dedicated page with a curated list of recommended
      accommodations near the event venue, complete with direct booking links. The site is fully
      responsive, optimized for all devices, and includes a custom domain featuring the couple's names.
      Hosting is included, and post-launch technical support ensures everything runs smoothly.
    </p>

    <div class="align-items-center flex flex-col gap-4 lg:flex-row">
      <div class="md:w-8/12">
        <img src={`${M}/bodalp-desktop2-960.avif`} class="border-round-xl w-full object-contain" alt="Boda Lis & Pavlos" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-center lg:w-4/12 lg:text-2xl">
        Share all your wedding details effortlessly with a personalized digital touch
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-row row1">
      <div class="grid-item"><img src={`${M}/bodalp-desktop3-960.avif`} alt="Boda Lis & Pavlos" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      <div class="grid-item"><img src={`${M}/bodalp-desktop4-960.avif`} alt="Boda Lis & Pavlos" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-row row2">
      <div class="grid-item"><img src={`${M}/bodalp-desktop7-960.avif`} alt="Boda Lis & Pavlos" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      <div class="grid-item"><img src={`${M}/bodalp-desktop8-960.avif`} alt="Boda Lis & Pavlos" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    </div>

    <div class="blp-left">
      <div class="project-card"><img src={`${M}/bodalp-desktop5-960.avif`} class="blp-placeholder" alt="Boda Lis & Pavlos RSVP form" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      <p>
        Guests can easily confirm their attendance through a personalized RSVP page that allows them to
        submit dietary preferences and song requests, with automated email confirmations for
        convenience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="blp-right">
      <p>
        A private administration page for the couple includes tools to manage guest responses, export
        RSVP data to Excel format, and track total attendance.
      </p>
      <div class="project-card"><img src={`${M}/bodalp-desktop6-960.avif`} class="blp-placeholder" alt="Boda Lis & Pavlos control panel" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .blp-card {
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }
  .blp-card-inner {
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .blp-card-inner {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
  .blp-card h2 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .blp-copy {
    font-family: 'Red Hat Text', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .blp-editorial :global(img):not(.first-project-image) {
    border: 2px var(--surface-muted) solid;
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }
  .blp-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }

  .grid-row {
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .row1,
  .row2 {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  }
  .grid-item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }

  .blp-left,
  .blp-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .blp-left {
    justify-content: left;
  }
  .blp-right {
    justify-content: right;
  }
  .blp-left > .project-card,
  .blp-right > .project-card {
    width: 70%;
  }
  .blp-left p,
  .blp-right p {
    width: 30%;
  }
  .blp-right p {
    text-align: right;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 970px) {
    .row1,
    .row2 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  @media screen and (max-width: 628px) {
    .blp-left,
    .blp-right {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .blp-left > .project-card,
    .blp-right > .project-card,
    .blp-left p,
    .blp-right p {
      width: unset;
    }
    .blp-left > .project-card {
      order: 2;
    }
    .blp-right p {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
